Please, see the Javadoc for the [ThreadPoolTaskExecutor.createQueue() method](https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/5.3.15/javadoc-api/org/springframework/scheduling/concurrent/ThreadPoolTaskExecutor.html#createQueue-int-) on the default queue factory method behaviour:

